  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Rvq8Ow69CYWHtjDWfgcpHHtXicnLgF9xFIyIcbJmgibV4av3QhJlNxGicavoV4NJpUMf4fcJD3wicpJ9pPicmXrdeyZnNUjxJsPRdXVbIvdlAnI4/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"505200604\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b262d5e5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FRvq8Ow69CYWHtjDWfgcpHHtXicnLgF9xFIyIcbJmgibV4av3QhJlNxGicavoV4NJpUMf4fcJD3wicpJ9pPicmXrdeyZnNUjxJsPRdXVbIvdlAnI4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; width: 100%;\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">3月16日，大英百科全书联合韦氏词典，起诉了OpenAI，并且罗列了ChatGPT的「四宗罪」。不要觉得Britannica心狠，此前ChatGPT编造错误信息，却把来源伪托给Britannica。OpenAI未作回应。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI又被起诉了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">3月16日，大英百科全书联合旗下的韦氏词典，对OpenAI提起诉讼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">原因是，它认为ChatGPT进行了大规模的版权侵权。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Britannica比所有原告准备得更充分：它紧抓训练数据抓取、模型记忆输出、RAG实时检索，同时追加《兰纳姆法》商标侵权。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是AI版权诉讼史上，第一次有人试图把整条生成链路一锅端。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">GPT-4能逐字默写大英百科</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据TechCrunch报道，Britannica直接点名GPT-4，认为它已经记住了其大量版权内容，能够按需输出近乎逐字逐句的复制品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不是相似，不是接近，是逐、字、复、制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这背后有一定的技术依据。斯坦福和耶鲁的研究团队曾做过实验，从主流大模型中提取《哈利·波特》原文，最高提取率达到96%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2048\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1280\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"351\" data-imgfileid=\"505200434\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2a384e8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYUubEKibGSFPlMLWTGHWncf9l58OXykXPia4w6hY45Psiaucicp7Nqiax7JGpiaTovmnkYOicfePCic0SsXCCvNc9EOLN8BBTyuwdXbr7Y%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也就是说，训练数据里的内容，有相当一部分被记在了模型权重里，在特定提示词下可以几乎原样还原。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Britannica持有的版权内容规模并不小。它旗下近</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">10万篇</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在线文章、百科条目和词典释义，覆盖从科学、历史到文学的几乎所有主要知识领域。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些内容由专业编辑和学科专家历经数十年积累而成。在维基百科崛起之前，这套体系就是人类知识的标准索引。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而OpenAI一直在灰色地带游走。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">查一次资料，也算侵权</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此前，各方一直在争论：用我的内容训练模型，算不算版权侵权？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Britannica这次的指控更进一步。他的指控分三层：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第一层</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，未经许可抓取近10万篇内容用于大模型训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第二层</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，ChatGPT在生成回答时，输出了Britannica内容的完整或部分逐字复制，这构成直接侵权。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第三层</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，也是最具争议的一层。OpenAI在ChatGPT的RAG工作流中使用了Britannica文章。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">RAG是ChatGPT扫描外部数据库、获取最新信息的机制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4404476418864908\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2502\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2502\" data-height=\"1102\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"248\" data-imgfileid=\"505200430\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b1428d8c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYX36YQuDiaSHmnPa1WqLbP2oPgXV4OuJtBbECib2kpvibX8GMIt4iaOhSiboGnzKv5TJw4aX2geV9NQkaBh6zfGVAwgbia6JG9AlKiaJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Britannica认为，即便它的内容没有进入训练集，但只要它出现在实时检索里，就被视为侵权。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种想法前所未有，它意味着不管是静态训练还是动态检索，只要调用了版权内容而未获授权，都要负责。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更有意思的是第四条指控：Lanham Act商标侵权。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Britannica认为，ChatGPT有时会产生幻觉，然后把这些错误内容归因于Britannica，制造Britannica生成了错误信息的假象。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这不单单是侵权，Britannica的品牌信誉都要替OpenAI的错误买单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这危及公众持续获取高质量、可信赖在线信息的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">同一个问题：德国说侵权，英国说没有</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是整场官司的核心，也是目前全球司法界争论最激烈的问题之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">德国慕尼黑法院在GEMA诉OpenAI案中认定：GPT-4和GPT-4o的模型权重中确实嵌入了歌词，这构成版权意义上的复制，可以提出禁令和赔偿请求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5581395348837209\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1376\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1376\" data-height=\"768\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"505200433\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cf19cda7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYVlGyENsGcvAr3sq3wDRzE6AMTGdOs3I0l0lbB0eRtafiboibxqMMbagH32oAerC4DUgqGNu4vz9xESOT4w1W0eTwKJp24b6Ug4w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型权重是AI在训练过程中学到的数值参数，它决定了模型会输出什么。在慕尼黑法院看来，只要能从这些参数里还原出作品就足以构成侵权。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">英国高等法院在Getty Images诉Stability AI案中得出了完全相反的结论。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7357910906298003\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1302\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1302\" data-height=\"958\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"414\" data-imgfileid=\"505200432\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5571a33c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYVeFKdg7AvgLtmL9LFlgibuuEib1txIwNwLLStpFiaTW6Z193fvPHyTDLuF2BfvQnbcH2JSW2s058UlaG82T7IHyA65Eia3nMlzMNs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI模型不是侵权副本，因为其权重既不包含也不复制版权作品本身，只存储了学习到的规律性模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">美国这边，Anthropic曾在版权诉讼中说服联邦法官William Alsup，认定将内容用作训练数据具有足够的转化性，可以适用合理使用原则。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但Alsup同时认定Anthropic非法下载了数百万本书而非付费获取，这一点构成违法，最终促成了</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">1.5亿美元</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">的集体和解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Britannica这起案子在纽约提起，适用的是美国联邦法律。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但目前没有确立性先例明确说明用版权内容训练LLM究竟算不算侵权，每起案子的结果，在相当程度上仍取决于具体法官的认定逻辑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果法院认可实时检索也构成侵权，那对整个AI行业的影响将远超任何一起训练数据纠纷。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">告Perplexity，是在给OpenAI热身</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这不是Britannica第一次出手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">早在2025年9月，Britannica就对Perplexity提起了类似的版权和商标侵权诉讼，该案目前仍在审理中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6583333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1200\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"790\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"370\" data-imgfileid=\"505200431\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2edbdbeb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYVxca6ia241HhXOhcBUUt4oEkrqvJMibhmUJnpjMyEVNdR2aNzjyhqUvGAfojN30ft4hRwHZaDBVAEN3WRJ8sO4xLo8TbwFSGCJY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Perplexity是一家以RAG为核心产品逻辑的AI搜索公司。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Britannica选择先打Perplexity，像是在做法律预演，摸清RAG侵权这条路的可行性，然后再把同样的逻辑复制到OpenAI身上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与此同时，行业里的版权战场正在全面升温。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">《纽约时报》、Ziff Davis、美国和加拿大十余家报纸先后起诉OpenAI。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3356940509915014\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1412\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1412\" data-height=\"474\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"189\" data-imgfileid=\"505200437\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bafad592&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYVuwXso7XneEM86p2IWnMicuHryqicWhrgELP3icxI9ictpWMSicTxcNaq6zMJ5UVbCzQic4Dwic3cnBp2uqFlNl0pnulmU7iapPaanR0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">The Intercept和US News &amp; World Report也已加入原告队伍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">截至目前，专门追踪AI版权诉讼的网站ChatGPT Is Eating The World统计显示，这已是针对OpenAI的</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第63起</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">版权诉讼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI对TechCrunch的置评请求未作回应。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">被维基百科打残，又被ChatGPT截流</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">退一步看，有些事情比赔偿金额更值得关注。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Britannica创立于1768年，是英文世界里持续时间最长的百科全书品牌，它代表的是几百年人类知识整理传统的某种象征。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当这样一个机构出现在AI版权诉讼的原告席上，传递的信号很清晰：知识权威这个概念，正在试图通过法律手段，重新在AI生态里划定自己的边界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Britannica曾是纸质百科时代的绝对权威，被维基百科打得几乎找不到存在感。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3356940509915014\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1412\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1412\" data-height=\"474\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"189\" data-imgfileid=\"505200435\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8945f4e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FRvq8Ow69CYUBwSVXDctjMawMk1jenMa2w4thu6A4vAyVCyZLeez7aGABdA9aTswsic6nVDnN80WB4oN3omGb7uKY0n1euVaVeNepB7yRm6icg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">后来转型为数字订阅平台，靠着内容的可信度和专业性重新站稳脚跟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如今，ChatGPT的出现让它又一次面临被替代的威胁——但不是被更好的百科替代，而是被一个用它内容训练出来、但不分给它一分钱的模型替代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">诉状里有一句话：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ChatGPT通过生成替代出版商内容的回复，抢走了出版商的流量。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是商业模式的正面冲突。RAG这条指控是否能站住脚，目前没有人能给出确定答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但如果法院哪天认可了这个逻辑，整个行业的实时检索管道都需要重新谈授权。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所有以联网搜索+AI生成为核心产品的公司，都要面临这样的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">250年的老牌百科，正在用一份诉状，尝试给AI的边界划一条线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这条线最终画在哪里？2026年，大概会有答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/encyclopedia-britannica-sues-openai-over-ai-training-2026-03-16/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/encyclopedia-britannica-sues-openai-over-ai-training-2026-03-16/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/03/16/merriam-webster-openai-encyclopedia-brittanica-lawsuit/\" target=\"_blank\">https://techcrunch.com/2026/03/16/merriam-webster-openai-encyclopedia-brittanica-lawsuit/</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://the-decoder.com/encyclopedia-britannica-sues-openai-for-training-on-nearly-100000-articles-without-permission/\" target=\"_blank\">https://the-decoder.com/encyclopedia-britannica-sues-openai-for-training-on-nearly-100000-articles-without-permission/</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://gizmodo.com/encyclopedia-britannica-sues-openai-over-ai-training-data-2000607770\" target=\"_blank\">https://gizmodo.com/encyclopedia-britannica-sues-openai-over-ai-training-data-2000607770</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://news.bloomberglaw.com/ip-law/britannica-merriam-webster-accuse-openai-of-copying-their-works\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.bloomberglaw.com/ip-law/britannica-merriam-webster-accuse-openai-of-copying-their-works</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://chatgptiseatingtheworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Encyclopedia_Britannica_Inc-v-OpenAI-COMPLAINT-Mar-13-2026.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://chatgptiseatingtheworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Encyclopedia_Britannica_Inc-v-OpenAI-COMPLAINT-Mar-13-2026.pdf</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.aol.com/articles/encyclopedia-britannica-sues-openai-over-141324436.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.aol.com/articles/encyclopedia-britannica-sues-openai-over-141324436.html</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "大英百科全书联合韦氏词典起诉 OpenAI，指控 ChatGPT 在训练数据抓取、模型记忆输出、RAG 实时检索三个层面构成版权侵权，并追加商标侵权，这是 AI 版权诉讼史上首次试图覆盖整条生成链路的案件。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "大英百科全书联合韦氏词典起诉 OpenAI，指控 ChatGPT 在训练数据抓取、模型记忆输出、RAG 实时检索三个层面构成版权侵权，并追加商标侵权，这是 AI 版权诉讼史上首次试图覆盖整条生成链路的案件。",
  "summary": "3 月 16 日，大英百科全书联合韦氏词典对 OpenAI 提起诉讼，指控 ChatGPT 进行大规模版权侵权。Britannica 提出四层指控：未经许可抓取近 10 万篇内容用于训练、逐字复制输出 Britannica 内容、RAG 实时检索中使用 Britannica 文章构成侵权、以及《兰纳姆法》商标侵权。Britannica 认为 GPT-4 已记住其大量版权内容可逐字输出，斯坦福和耶鲁研究显示从主流大模型中提取《哈利·波特》原文提取率高达 96%。文章对比了德国慕尼黑法院认定模型权重嵌入歌词构成侵权、与英国 Getty Images 案得出相反结论的冲突，以及 Anthropic 1.5 亿美元集体和解的案例。截至目前这已是针对 OpenAI 第 63 起版权诉讼。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Britannica 首次把整条生成链路一锅端，从训练数据抓取、模型记忆输出到 RAG 实时检索全面起诉。",
      "explanation": "这是 AI 版权诉讼史上第一次有原告试图覆盖静态训练和动态检索两个环节，如 RAG 指控成立将影响整个 AI 行业的实时检索管道。"
    },
    {
      "point": "GPT-4 能逐字复制 Britannica 内容，斯坦福耶鲁研究证实主流大模型对版权内容提取率高达 96%。",
      "explanation": "模型权重中确实嵌入了大量版权内容，在特定提示词下可原样还原，这为版权侵权提供了技术依据。"
    },
    {
      "point": "全球司法界对训练 AI 是否侵权尚无定论，德国认定侵权，英国认定不侵权，美国判例不一。",
      "explanation": "慕尼黑法院认定模型权重嵌入歌词构成侵权，英国 Getty Images 案得出相反结论，Anthropic 案以 1.5 亿美元和解，每起案件结果仍取决于具体法官认定。"
